text: There are two predefined services In the Services tab Order Service and Supervision. Note! The Services tab is only available in real-time workflows. Open Workflow Properties - Services tab Button Description Button Description Add Service Click to select a service to be used by the workflow, then click OK to apply it. Remove Service Visible when a service has been selected. Click to remove the service from the workflow. Subsections This section contains the following subsections: Ordered Service Supervision Service
